INSERT INTO `tbl_activities` VALUES (5,'Trekking','Beautiful View Comes After the Hardest Climbs','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Adventure tours banner-min.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/dtl-bnr.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/73.jpg','Popular Trekking  Destinations In India','Climb the mountains, embrace the challenge, feel the fresh air and behold the view. Trek through the valleys, slog through the lush grass and rich soil, learn and explore. Pick from the hand curated trekking trials for an opulent outdoor experience.','The frozen lake treks to the desert crossing expeditions, and the awe inspiring valleys of northeast to the impenetrable forests of Western Ghats, India is an abode for trekking freaks.',1,'','',1),(6,'Kayaking','Experience the calmness of Shallow Water','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/kayak-984566_19201.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/boats-canoe-group-696039.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/HAWK (7).jpg','Popular Kayaking Points In India','Paddle and explore the deep blue waters in the best way possible. Experience the great water from a different perspective and fed its heartbeat when rowing on a kayak through the marine. Take your paddles, row through the picturesque natural beauty, and inspire others.','Water your adventure spirits and paddle your way to great endless fun in the great waters of India. Find yourself under a fresh canopy, gliding over a fish, sun kissed, all in a place of natural beauty.',2,'hhh','sss',1),(7,'Paragliding','Explore the Sykes ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/paragliding-3692079_19201.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/para1.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/75.jpg','Major Paragliding Points In India','Fly above the clouds and fulfill that old childhood dream of flying free like an eagle. Flying high is everyone’s dream and it was our childhood fantasy to fly above the clouds like an eagle. Fulfill this dream in a spine-chilling adventure which is one of the most popular air adventure on this planet. Fasten your straps and scream loud where the misty clouds will embrace you.','Our country, known for its mighty mountain ranges is an abode for the high flyers. Ranging from the great Himalayas to the Western Ghats, it hosts many such destinations which offers great flying experiences for those who have a love for the clouds. Find out here which sky you want to explore.',3,'ffff','ss',1),(9,'White Water Rafting','Raft through the wilderness of water','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/river-rafting-960158_1920.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/rafting-2033494_19201.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/45.jpg','Popular White Water Rafting Points In India','The actively flowing river, the sudden flash of the chilled waters, and the extreme rush of adventure, what else you need to paddle down the quick rapidness of our country which gifts us one of the best experiences of as lifetime. Discover the white water rafting in and across the country in its wild waters.','There is very few destinations where the real and original white water rafting can be done. But when its done the amount of adrenaline it pumps out is exorbitant. Every waters behave way different than other and that itself is the beauty of rafting in the country’s wildly white waters.',5,'dd','dd',1),(16,'Biking','Experience the biking','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/HAWK (5)3.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/HAWK (2).jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/57.jpg','Popular Biking Points in India','Test','Testing',6,'','',1),(17,'Bungee Jumping','Bungee Jumping','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/bridge-664131_19202.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/bungee-436750_1920.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/25.jpg','Popular Bungee Jumps Over India','tt','ff',7,'d','h',1),(18,'Skiing   ','Skiing in the glacial mountains ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/mountaineerz-1143556_1920.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/trekking-1742821_19201.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/28.jpg','test','test','test',8,'m','jn',1),(19,'Scuba Diviing','Explore the Seabed !!','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/diving-813028_1920.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/divers-681516_1920.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/diver-664654_1920.jpg','Popular Scuba Diving Points In India','Plunge into the ocean and discover the surprising marine life. These handpicked scuba diving tours let you explore country’s best oceans in its depth. Wear the mask, take a deep breath and dive! Swim underwater along the wonderful creations underwater.','The ocean is always beautiful, mysterious, wild and free. These popular destinations are the best kept secrets of the water. Dive deep in, try caressing a fish, get amazed by the colors underwater and thus, explore it in a whole. ',9,'f','f',1);
