INSERT INTO `tbl_destination` VALUES (9,'Munnar','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Webp1.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/munar.jpg',NULL,'ddd','Even if it is a Leisure , Fun or Adventure plan to Munnar ,feel the comfort of being in a total holiday without any worries and select from our range of hand crafted holiday experiences','Stays in Munnar is as unique as the destination itself.When its the experiential stays, the experience is exponential .Explore the best of the stays here','Munnar is one of the major adventure showcase of Kerala.From light treks to paragliding on the mountain valleys of Munnar, it has a very broad range of activities to choose from.Select.. Book..and Experience something new','ee','Munnar..!! The Kashmir of South India !!',1,2),(10,'Kashmir','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Neelum_Valley_Azad_Jammu__Kashmir_Pakistan.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/kashmir4.jpg',NULL,'ff','Experience the heaven on earth in all its glory.Explore the nook and corner of Kashmir through our specially designed tours.Lets fall in love once again in the valley of Himalayas,sun kissed peaks,snow filled adventures,monasteries of divine charm.There is a lot irresistible experience here which a true traveler cannot miss.','From the houseboats of the Dal lake to the tented stays in Nubra valley, the collection of stay experience here is mind blowing.Check and explore the one you wish to be in.','The region which is home for great terrains like Zanskar, Nubra, Leh ,Gulmarg  ,Sonmarg,Pahalgam etc. are major activity filled tourism destinations in the country .One who loves to explore the rare has all in it.','ff','Kashmir - The Heaven on Earth',1,3),(11,'Meghalaya','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Webp.net-compress-image.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/meghalaya.jpg',NULL,'kk','The Gods abode Meghalaya is one of  a must visit destination in India.It hosts a huge concentration of natural beauty coupled with unique experiences.Its cultural rich festivals and mysterious beauty of valleys makes it favorite for an explorer to find his souls.','The region where bed and breakfast establishments shows its dominance. Meghalaya  do have wide range of experiential stays to execute a wanderers plan more fabulous .Explore Gods abodes experiential stays with us.','Meghalaya is not just a wanderers choice ,but a locale for adventure junkies to freak out,  where unique experiences can be explored like caving in Synrang,Dawki river trek etc.Its not onlyjust Godes abode but a haven for adventure enthusiasts. ','ll','Meghalaya - Gods Abode',1,7),(13,'Manali','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/manali-solang-valley-147549233805-orijgp.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/manali6.jpg',NULL,'jj','One of the most traveled destination in the country, nestled in the mighty Himalayas often called as the Valley of Gods . This place is famous for its abundant natural beauty which makes it a dream destination for many travelers.Whether it be the temples, monasteries, nature, weather or the adventure activities, Manali has a lot to offer.','The hospitality of this Himalayan town is jaw dropping. From snow cottages to luxury resorts, Manali has great accommodation facilities which offers sky high standard services.Browse which one would you choose from here..','Manali can be considered as the adventure capital of the country for its variety of activities the destination offer.Activities for the children to spine chilling adventure for the trained adventurers , Manali is an asylum for those who love the rush of adrenaline .','nn','Manali - The valley of Gods !!',1,1),(15,'Alappuzha','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Webp5.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/alappy2.jpg',NULL,'ss','The world famous backwaters of Kerala is a world in itself. Backwaters, village experiences, farm tours…. A whirlwind of uniquely crafted magnificent natural beauty. Browse through your favorite tours and book the best.','Alleppey, as it is popularly called has myriad options to stay and experience the place at its best. Discover life in the banks of the backwaters and live the unique life which only Alleppey can offer.','Tired by land adventures? What about trying something in the waters? Chose from the number of activities that can be tried n tested in the shallow waters pf Alleppey and trust us, there is a lot to uncover. ','ss','Experience the Venice of East  ',1,5),(16,'Goa','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/beach-1867137_960_720.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/goa4.jpg',NULL,'aa','A blend of Portuguese and Indian influences, Goa is the most energetic tourist destination in the country. Famous for its awe inspiring beaches and the landscape, it is a real gem. Goa is more than perfect to be a beach destination which hosts a whole lot of activities near to its shore. Popular as a hippie destination, the tourist flow to goa is always on the rise due to highly electrifying character it owns.','As one of the top biodiversity hotspots, goa is blessed with immense natural resources and hence stays are as unique as the destination is. Explore stay options varying from shacks to the jungle houses in this divine land.','There is a whole lot of options for a traveler to keep themselves active on their vacations. From forest trials to water adventure, the options are vivid. One will be confused when exploring these activities and forget not, its uniqueness overloaded. ','aa','Goa - The Tourist Paradise !!',NULL,4),(18,'Hyderabad','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/char.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/hyderabad.jpg',NULL,'ss','Test','Keep Testing','Keep testing testing','sss','Experience the city of Pearls',NULL,9),(19,'Wayanad','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Wyanad1.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/wayanad1.jpg',NULL,'Wayanad','test','Stays in Wayanad is as unique as the destination itself.When its the experiential stays, the experience is exponential .Explore the best of the stays here','test','Wayanad','Experience the Wilderness of Wayanad',1,10),(20,'Thekkady','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/thekkadyslider.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/049130598Thekkady_Main.jpg',NULL,'Thekkady','test','Discover your apt living from our collection of experiential stays across Thekkady is sure to give you a holiday worth remembering.','tst','Thekkady','Thekkady..The Land of Spices',1,8),(22,'Kerala','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/clouds-cloudy-countryside-236047.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/tea-garden-1751083_960_7201.jpg',NULL,'gg','Test','Test','Test','hh','Gods Own Country',NULL,11),(24,'Darjeeling ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/darjeeling-197611_960_720.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/darjeeling-197611_960_7201.jpg',NULL,'d','Test','Test','Test','d','Darjeeling - Sikkim Experiences',NULL,12),(26,'Kochi','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/fort-kochi-1483460289.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/fort_kochi20131031104449_422_1.jpg',NULL,'Kochi','Test','Discover Experiential Stays, Vacation Rentals, Villas, Homestays,  Offbeat Holiday Cottages and unique heritage stays for family and group from our collection of experiential stays across in Kochi is sure to give you a holiday worth remembering.','test','Kochi','Kochi - Queen of Arabian Sea ',1,6),(27,'Athirappilly ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/1200px-Athirapally_Water_falls.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Athirapally.jpg',NULL,'n','Test','test','test','n','Athirappilly - The land of Waterfalls',NULL,13),(28,'Rajasthan','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Gadisar-Lake-in-Rajasthan..jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/travel-to-rajasthan-feature-image_0.jpg',NULL,'nn','Test','tEST','Test','mm','The Land of Royals',NULL,14),(29,'Rishikesh','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/rafting-687370_1920.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/temple-1166023_1920.jpg',NULL,'r','test','test','test','r','Rishikesh - The land of Adventure ',NULL,15),(31,'Trivandrum','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/How-to-reach-Trivandrum.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/The-Leela-Kovalam---Facade.JPG',NULL,'Tvm','','','Discover the wide range of activities that can be explored by any adventure junkies through us.','Tvm','The Capital of Kerala',NULL,16);
