INSERT INTO `tbl_exp_stays` VALUES (2,'Tree houses','Experience the woods','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/tree-min.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/main-banner.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/50.jpg','Popular Tree House Destinations In India','Ever thought living in a comfort up above from the ground? What about experiencing nature from a different perspective or may be from a birds eye view? Well, that is tree house for you! The very historic way of jungle living is one of current era’s most sought after experience.','Step out and explore the world and live in a perfect blend with nature in these cozy tree houses spread across the country. Perfect tree houses for your perfect holiday experiences.',1,'f','f',1,1),(3,'Tent Camping','Experience the Outdoors..','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/nature-3125452_19202.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/adventure-camp-camping-6995587.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/adventure-alps-camp-618848.jpg','Popular Tent Camping Destinations In India','Discovering the unknown by staying outdoors is the new style of exploring the unexplored and the most perfect way is camping. Popular across the globe, it does have a huge fan following in our country too. Who doesn’t want to sit alone in the woods gazing at the stars in the middle of the night. Isn’t it.','Different places, different woods, different ambience, different people, different culture and hence, different experience. We have clubbed in a number of camping destinations across the country and believe, each one will be a new for you.',1,'nbnb','c  ',2,1),(4,'Forest Stays','Stay Wild..Stay Safe..','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/cabin-1081733_960_720.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/masinagudi.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/37.jpg','Hand Picked Forest Stay Experiences in India','Stay in the cradle of nature when living in these forest stays. Fall in love with the chirping birds, cuddle with the aromatic breeze and relish the thick green around you.','Forests cannot be the same everywhere. Each forest has got its own nature, its own character and its own uniqueness. So try staying in these vivid living forest cabins deep inside the woods to realize what experiential living is.',2,'ffff','ll',3,1),(5,'Cottages','The Private Experiential Cabins..!! ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/ambady-111.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/garden-302259_960_720.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/38.jpg','Popular Cottage Experiences in India','Cottage experience teaches us the ‘art’ of doing nothing. These cabins are those facilities which offers ultimate peace away from the chaotic everyday life. Any such escapes planned can be perfect if lives in these cottages.','Explore the places and live in these cabins thus executing a picture-perfect escape. The energy each destination emits will make us wish to stay there forever.',3,'','',1,1),(6,'Heritage Bungalows ','Experience the bit of Heritage Luxury !!','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/country-house-540796_960_7203.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/133_aboutslider21.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/20170225111732AMHM4.jpg','Popular Heritage Bungalow Destinations of India','Ever dreamed of living in the luxury which the iconic royal empires used to live. Check out the list of such opulent living spaces from the handpicked castles spread across the country. Experience the original authentic luxury living and the pride of history.','Be it the royal forts of Rajputs or the mansion bungalows of the British, the exorbitant luxury is always in its peak when stayed in these experiential stays. Pick your stay here and experience the magical opulence of the past.',1,'','',1,1),(7,'Home Stays','The Home away from Homes ..!!','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/home stay.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/cottage-1689224_960_720.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/36.jpg','Handpicked Home Stays Experience in India','Be influenced by our unique collection of home stays across the country. Learn new languages, experience distinct people, take a glimpse into the past and cook some food. A lot to do in these handpicked homes.','People in each destination is different. So are their homes. Much different from other holiday homes. The moods vary, ambiance differ and the experience will be unique. So, explore from the popular destinations.',2,'','',1,1),(8,'Plantation Stays','Live Out in the Midst of Plantations','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/43.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/Dreamcatcher-resort-munnar-teaplantation.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/48.jpg','Popular Plantation Stays Destinations of India','Think about sipping hot coffee sitting in midst of a tea plantation with the sweet aroma of tea leaves seducing your nozzles and that naughty wind plays with your hair. Explore more such out of the world experiences here.','Every place is unique and so is every experience. Discuss the best of the plantation experience and give it a shot. We are sure you are gonna love it.Explore more such out of the world experiences here.',3,'','',3,1),(9,'Farm Stays','Unique Nestles in the Midst of Farms ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/vineyard-3757669_960_7205.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/vineyard-3757669_960_7204.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/40.jpg','Popular Farm Stays Destinations of India','Live more close to the mother nature on your expert crafted stays in the most loved farms. Plant a tree, do some farming, learn about a new species and start loving our earth more, much more.','Imagine living a life where we live in the midst of fresh grown yield, having organically prepared food in a home grown environment. This is what it feels to be in these places and we realize that the life over there is the authentic one. ',4,'','',1,1),(10,'Water Front Villas','Water Front Villas','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/20170225111816AMlakefrontvill.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/20170130090751AMAboutIntro.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/20170323191312PM_MG_7758crop.jpg','Test','test','test',5,'l','l',1,1),(11,'House Boats','Houseboats - The Floating Palace ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/cnmjlelnoiigioba.png','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/houseboat1 (2)2.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/20170628060353AMSpiceCoastCruisesAboutSlider4.jpg','Popular Houseboat Points in India','Being of shallow draft, the houseboats have living quarters in the superstructure, with large windows giving plenty of light and ventilation and  typically have broad decks, making them ideal summer homes.','Browse through our collection of handpicked houseboats across the country',6,'h','h',3,1);
