INSERT INTO `tbl_pkg_category` VALUES (1,'SPECIAL INTEREST TOURS','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/19.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/sit2.jpg','Special Interest Tours','Special Interest Tours','Hawks Made  Special Interest Tours','Ever traveled somewhere only to explore and experience something unique...? When was the last time you did something for the first time..? Haven\'t you planned something specific on your tour but cancelled only because your executor didn\'t offer that service..? So.. its time to rise up , and travel to explore our little but unimaginably big fantasies. Find that one thing that excites you..tell us what it is.. travel with us and explore it with your heart and soul.','Find from our list of some of the most sought after Special Interest Tours. Discover the world in your own style and travel for what you love . We have handpicked some tours to suit your Special Interest and this country has a lot more to offer.',NULL,2),(2,'ADVENTURE TOURS','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/23.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/adventure.jpg','Adventure Tours','Adventure Tours','Hawks Made Adventure Experiences','Incredibly rich in breathtaking topography, India is a place of infinite offerings! Seasons, climate, landscape or anything that you could name; every corner of the country differs in all senses with the other. This uniqueness of the regions makes India a hub of innumerable activities! Whether you hate it or love it, but Summer is definitely one season which opens up a lot of doors in our lives! One such door is the door of adventure activities that the high-spirited chunks are always in search of.','Having been blessed with nature’s bounty, India can successfully siege to all the demands of these adrenaline junkies seeking that quick rush of blood! If you are one of such type and are open to every kind of adventure, you could try your hands on with us!',NULL,4),(3,'KERALA WEEKEND PLANS','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/41.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/kerala2.jpg','Kerala Weekend Plans','Kerala Weekend Plans','Kerala Weekend Getaways ','Say good bye to your work week tensions and say hello to one of the coolest weekend.Celebrate your weekends  not just for the sake of it, but for the high intensity fun it reacts out. A break is always much needed for us to shoo away the worldly hustle and bustle and to escape into the verdant welcoming mother nature.So plan an escape , execute it and blow of the steam. ','Kerala is a perfect getaway for anyone who wants to invest their weekends in travel.It displays a whole lot of options ranging from Campsites to luxury resorts to activities and adventures of all level, all placed perfectly in a marvelously unique landscape.After a hectic work week , Kerala can be your impeccable \'out of the world\' weekend destination, to throw away the worries and get recharged for the new week.',NULL,1),(4,'FAVORITE HOLIDAY EXPERIENCES ','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/31.jpg','http://holidayhawks.in/uploads/fav.jpg','Favorite Holiday Experiences','Special Interest Tours','Top Rated Holidaying Experiences in India','Explore the favorite holiday destinations in India with specially curated experiences from the experienced team.Top rated holiday picks that everyone must take in India.Experience the favorite handpicked tours  from Holidayhawks ','Top rated holiday picks that everyone must take in India.Experience the favorite handpicked tours  from Holidayhawks',NULL,3);
